com.mindfusion.scheduling.awt

Class PreviewTextKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mindfusion.scheduling.awt.PreviewTextKey

  • public final class PreviewTextKey
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the key for various texts in the built-in Print Preview form.

    Members of this enumeration can be used as keys in the getCustomPreviewTexts dictionary of the PrintOptions class.
